{"tid":1633723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭在笑，共狗在叫，我「屌眾人」阿","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:22:21.000Z","uid":219681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"186f26ab5f30220ddbfd6d845f079e7ae9d5ee25","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:59:57.000Z","msg":"你班友，一個行動Post 都冇，響度嘈嘈嘈，好心你地啦，咪以為連登就等於全世界啦<br />\n任何時候，都要有獨立批判思考，唔係入去個Post，見人地有2000+ 個Like 就未睇Like左先<br />\n醒少少，而家呢度既Mon Post 狗同五毛閒閒地都5-6百隻啦，未睇曬就唔好爭住留言推Post 出醜<br />\n<br />\n我簡單總結下啦，都廢事咁長氣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一. 「真勇武」呢個時間一定係休息緊，唔會上黎講咩又失望又盛囉</span></span><br />\n知唔知尋晚人地搞到幾點阿，又要逃走又要搵手足仲要做哨，幾多人返唔到屋企，電話都搞到冇曬電，邊個會咁得閒上黎開Post<br />\n仲有，人地要出擊，唔駛響度話定你地知。醒下啦，連登已經唔係一個發放消息既安全地方，某程度上佢已經俾敵人入侵左啦。仲要加埋你地班豬隊友，睇下直播，再黎睇兩睇留言就知道個風向，唔該你收皮啦，驗下個腦再返黎睇下大家同唔同Level<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">二. 前線係唔會有「左膠」架。</span></span><br />\n大愛左膠連條蟲都唔敢踩啦，邊敢行到咁前。勸你地停手係廢事打能死左佢益左人地，明唔明。「羞辱」「錫春袋」大把野玩，以武制暴，而唔係以暴亦暴，前線手足其實好清楚，你班花生友就咪咁多廢話啦。我地又唔能係黑警，藍絲，如果要隊林佢，拖埋一二角，冇記者影到，直接用刀啦。咁多個月啦，搵把刀好難咩? 有冇見過兄弟用刀斬人阿 ? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">三. 「和理非」「文宣組」冇一刻停過。</span></span><br />\n而家資訊量係極多，已經係去到追唔切既程度啦。好心你班友仔，檢討下自己有咩幫到手。你唔係以為「出過黎行」就叫左幫左手下話? 要解鎖文宣成就，你起碼都要整番張長輩圖先啦。咪下下響度等人搞，人地搞完Like 左就當做左。有冇幫人印出黎阿，有冇幫手貼阿，咩都冇，就唔好話自己做「文宣。啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">四. 知唔知咩係「去毒」，「洗太平地」。</span></span><br />\n點解 Facebook d 裝修Post 咁多人話多謝黑警，屌你唔係傻能左覺得做完野要爭住認係自己做下話，咁你不如直接去自首啦。人地用自己方式洗地，又唔係洗俾你睇，你睇完笑下咪算囉，又要話人地抹煞你既功勞。唔好傻啦，唔通我屋企收埋支AK又要話你知咩? 都係果句啦，臥底唔一定係「黑警」架，可以係「真。黑社會」黎架。前線手足一早已經搵左方法組隊同埋防止呢D情況出現，唔會話你地知「How」囉，係支持既，就響前線撤退既時候落街做街坊，做哨，做司機。唔係就收皮，打個J，然後早D抖。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五. 咩為之過火?</span></span><br />\n屌，前線影相就唔駛講啦，講左十世啦，仲影就抵屌啦。屌下你又唔係打柒你，我地有教養架，知道咩係可為咩係不可為，真係過左火既，做錯既，唔駛講，即刻幫手足「消毒」。你睇下爆富臨果陣，唔小心嚇親人，一張紙巾成件事就唔同曬啦。<br />\n尋日掟中記者就緊係唔好睇啦，真手足又好，假手足都好，大家都唔想架。咁應該點做阿，去港台度留言對唔住同辛苦記者，去醫院送生果又得，咁個畫面咪平衡囉。黑警射鳩完我地都識出黎支持伙記啦，你班友反而響度屌屌屌，無能聊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唉，一邊打呢個Post，一邊食早餐，又浪費左我D時間<br />\n知唔知呢一刻幾多手足響臭格俾人搞緊<br />\n幾多律師幫緊手足搵料<br />\n見到你地咁易俾人帶黎帶去，真係So sad，恥與為伍阿<br />\n如果冇獨立思考果D，唔好睇連登啦，去睇Baby condom 啦，反正睇聽完人地講一句，又會「係阿係阿」架啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"87719a959871e076b3a809c4e2c1faeefd41a9e7","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5c22a40bcec5f90a347aa8a6373ac58bea6bbd","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"連Post 都要自己推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9614c51cd30bc146835caadcae8160c2796a9b22","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4731e6a8b195716d2992d139ee32e88afeaf031","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f4ad9b441ba64c26e94a1ed4457d52ff12a67","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6c0942e0307e4c978c1e145f6c8e6581b2f75a","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5404fe52cd647fb8a991cdef1ffd44ac7dd143a7","tid":1633723,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4085d2ea88660e9f849aaa07ef9290df5e686a2d","tid":1633723,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"573b766b6c1784627ee2a97d0f659bedc3711472","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cdef349562b645d7508de53f9d8fb5af7e5e61","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f7e11d03115c311f2cd8495965997d194b9567","tid":1633723,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"1cfb0038bce1f1b9fac973b1eacaa41bc64fc92f","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d82ec5d03379710bab3cf2b91cef694c3579466","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0826d91b3e3401484450d67a4133c4a3f1d4771c","tid":1633723,"uid":314165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>六月至今，當權者做左好多野令我地處於水深火熱之中<br />\n裝潢交通，商鋪，基建，受苦只會係我地市民，d高官，落order個個會幫手搞番掂咩，唔會！咪又係叫d基層員工幫他們執屎，通宵工作，破壞港鐵會阻到d高官出入咩，佢哋出入都揸車，點會有影響</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">反而只會令外國報導/遊客以為香港好亂，示責我地，明明我地係受苦的一群，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>我地要令所有人都知道香港人仍然係好理性，係好安全既地方，呢個係我地既核心價值</ins></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>宜家好多外資都澈左去新加坡，又被人發旅遊警示，跟本係坐收漁人之利，難道我地要眼白白要睇住自己辛辛苦苦建立既野，供手送俾人？！</ins></strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人同內地既唔同係我地係食腦，靠智慧取勝，係文明的一群，過度既裝修，私了，咪搞到我地好似俾大陸同化左(用血腥和暴力)<br />\n俾更加多機會班黑警,無能政府做我地黑材料</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>攬炒香港對林鄭根本都冇影響，她都搵埋不少，唔做特首，咪拎埋d錢去其他地方過世界<br />\n到時受苦只會係我地呢班真真正正既香港人</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n所以，要爭取，但唔係用暴力，而係係世界不同大型平台發表言論，對他們施壓</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"25c169b993b624a26e06434f636e7d1d156e0560","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bad41e7f9e63299a5b3427cb71b77408b11791","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a520615674a3ecffa5797bf57f529bcf829e71","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf7a5d75bab5766d76fff07a7c87872c90e3e66","tid":1633723,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face